{"type":null,"faqId":9138,"title":"Mate2(MT2-L01/L02)WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">这个问题是休眠策略的问题。进入的方法：在主屏幕，点击</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">无线和网络</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"> </span></b><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">&gt; <b>WLAN</b></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，再点击菜单键并进入<b>高级</b></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">在休眠状态下保持</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">WLAN</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">连接</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，设置为</span><b><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">“</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">始终</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">”</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"> </span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29625\" /></span> \n</p>\n&nbsp;\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">注：手机默认设置是始终，也就是一直可以正常连接。如果调整休眠策略就会使得在待机时自动断开。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">个选项的含义如下：</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">始终</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">：一直保持</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">WLAN</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">的连接。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">仅限充电时</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">：只有在充电时才一直保持连接，如果不充电，待机后</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">分钟断开连接。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">从不</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">（会增加数据网络流量）：待机后</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">分钟断开连接。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9724","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396233055000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":32,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}